        <source>jssTimeStamp(): TimeStamp;
// --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:		04 February 2003 by cnwdad1
//
// Purpose:		This reimplementation returns a null value since a time stamp value
//				is not relevant in the context of this control.
